        <abstract>
            <p>Has several specimens illustrating dimorphism in insects that he would be happy to leave where CD could examine them.</p> 
<p>Discusses the ant genera <hi rend="italic">Formica</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Atta</hi>, and the origin of the two forms of workers commonly found in the species of these genera.</p> 
        </abstract>
